title: Pacific Rim
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Chinese, Japanese, Thai, Salad bar, Beer/Wine, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Located in the Arapahoe basin cafeteria. Has many vegan dishes including Asian bowls with white rice, fresh veggies, tofu, and choice of one of four kinds of vegan sauces: coconut curry, chili garlic, sweet spicy plum, or zesty orange. Uses designated woks just for vegan food.
